<section
  class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-20 pb-24 overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-[#0f172a]"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-center text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 animate-on-scroll"
      data-animation="fade-in-up"
    >
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-1.5 mb-6 rounded-full bg-[#6324eb]/10 border border-[#6324eb]/20"
      >
        <span
          class="text-sm font-bold text-[#6324eb] tracking-wide uppercase font-display"
          >¿Por qué TodoConta AI?</span
        >
      </div>
      <h2
        class="text-[#111827] dark:text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight pb-3 font-display m-0"
      >
        ¿Por qué este reto es diferente?
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-[#6B7280] dark:text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mt-4 leading-relaxed m-0"
      >
        La mayoría de cursos te dan teoría genérica. Nosotros te damos
        herramientas estratégicas para automatizar y facturar más.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Grid Section -->
    <div class="max-w-[1024px] mx-auto">
      <div
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-x-12 md:gap-y-10"
      >
        <!-- Feature 1: Robot -->
        <div
          class="group flex flex-col items-start gap-5 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/10 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[#6324eb]/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 animate-on-scroll"
          data-animation="scale-in"
          data-delay="0"
        >
          <div
            class="h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6324eb] to-[#2563EB] flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-[#6324eb]/20 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shrink-0"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-[32px]"
              >smart_toy</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-left">
            <h3
              class="text-[#111827] dark:text-white text-xl font-bold leading-tight font-display m-0"
            >
              No es Solo ChatGPT
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-[#4B5563] dark:text-gray-300 text-base font-normal leading-relaxed m-0"
            >
              Dominarás el uso estratégico de 4 herramientas: ChatGPT, Claude,
              Gemini y Perplexity. Aprenderás cuándo usar cada una según la
              tarea.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 2: Brain -->
        <div
          class="group flex flex-col items-start gap-5 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/10 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[#6324eb]/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 animate-on-scroll"
          data-animation="scale-in"
          data-delay="100"
        >
          <div
            class="h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6324eb] to-[#2563EB] flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-[#6324eb]/20 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shrink-0"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-[32px]"
              >psychology</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-left">
            <h3
              class="text-[#111827] dark:text-white text-xl font-bold leading-tight font-display m-0"
            >
              Mentalidad IA-First
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-[#4B5563] dark:text-gray-300 text-base font-normal leading-relaxed m-0"
            >
              Aprenderás a pensar estratégicamente para resolver problemas
              complejos, no solo a copiar y pegar prompts. Framework de 3
              preguntas aplicable a cualquier situación.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 3: Flag (Localized) -->
        <div
          class="group flex flex-col items-start gap-5 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/10 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[#6324eb]/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 animate-on-scroll"
          data-animation="scale-in"
          data-delay="200"
        >
          <div
            class="h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6324eb] to-[#2563EB] flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-[#6324eb]/20 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shrink-0"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-[32px]"
              >flag</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-left">
            <h3
              class="text-[#111827] dark:text-white text-xl font-bold leading-tight font-display m-0"
            >
              Casos 100% Reales Mexicanos
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-[#4B5563] dark:text-gray-300 text-base font-normal leading-relaxed m-0"
            >
              Ejemplos tropicalizados para contabilidad mexicana: SAT, CFDI,
              RESICO, nóminas y normativa fiscal actual. Cero teoría genérica de
              otros países.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Feature 4: Money (ROI) -->
        <div
          class="group flex flex-col items-start gap-5 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-gray-100 dark:border-white/10 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-[#6324eb]/10 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 animate-on-scroll"
          data-animation="scale-in"
          data-delay="300"
        >
          <div
            class="h-16 w-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6324eb] to-[#2563EB] flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-[#6324eb]/20 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shrink-0"
          >
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-[32px]"
              >work</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-left">
            <h3
              class="text-[#111827] dark:text-white text-xl font-bold leading-tight font-display m-0"
            >
              Aplicación Inmediata
            </h3>
            <p
              class="text-[#4B5563] dark:text-gray-300 text-base font-normal leading-relaxed m-0"
            >
              Cada caso práctico es aplicable desde el día siguiente con tus
              clientes reales. Enfoque en resultados tangibles, no en teoría
              abstracta.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .font-display {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk Variable', 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  }
</style>
